Detailed Description

cvmx_sriomaint::_erb_lt_dev_id_capt

This register contains error information. It is locked when a logical/transport error is detected and unlocked when the SRIOMAINT()_ERB_LT_ERR_DET is written to zero. This register should be written only when error detection is disabled.
